  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566213913-LUMYSXYP7MIR3QTU7DZJ/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Recently we got to attend the cutest pop-up hosted by my friend Pamelyn from <a href=\"https://www.shopbasheryandco.com/\">Bashery &amp; Co</a> in Playa Vista as an early Valentine's Day celebration. Of course I'm always looking for any excuse to get dressed up and smooch my favorite little guy!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566250464-VR5QQ5EB13YFYCCEXWGK/7b-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7c-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566248891-GS0WVL475VMC9E9PCDAX/7c-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566472799-1Q1ZZ6KA3VE5VMQIA604/7d-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>There were so many great vendors including <a href=\"http://www.travelingphotobus.com/\">The Traveling Photo Bus</a>,  <a href=\"http://eventivemoments.com/\">Eventive Moments</a>,  <a href=\"http://www.funkyletterboutique.com/\">Funky Letter Boutique</a>, and the coolest group of mamas!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7e-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566289444-A3AD3FZH3LECAOTMBQZ2/7e-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566293058-KX1U129ZFG9YG32HV90R/7f-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566295997-5OKVBW2G2WMC64QPKS01/7g-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7h-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566296877-5ISHVU1X2TSGOQPXB9EE/7h-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7i-Kissing+Booth+Event+_+Amy+Tangerine.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590566513328-H9YLDXDQ2P5EVI8EXZE2/7i-Kissing%2BBooth%2BEvent%2B_%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I wore a dress from Rent The Runway (I'm obsessed right now with their unlimited subscription - more on that soon). Jack's clothes are from <a href=\"http://bit.ly/amykidbox\">Kidbox</a>. To receive 20% off your first order, use the code JACK20 at checkout. Would make an awesome present for Valentine's Day!</p><p>Photos by <a href=\"https://www.ographr.com/\">Ographr</a></p>"
